title: Def Leppard - [2006] Yeah! [320kbs] ~~Renovatio~~
description:
Yeah! is an album of cover versions of 1970s rock hits, recorded by Def Leppard. It is the first cover album by the band. It was originally to be released on 20 September 2005, but it was announced on 31 March 2006 that the album would be released on 23 May 2006. 

The album was delayed numerous times and was met with mixed reviews upon its eventual release. The album charted at No. 16 on The Billboard 200# and No. 52 on the UK Albums Chart.
